{"id":371,"date":"2021-12-28T12:03:00","date_gmt":"2021-12-28T10:03:00","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/?p=371"},"modified":"2022-10-03T16:21:28","modified_gmt":"2022-10-03T13:21:28","slug":"artificial-intelligence-in-corporate-cloud-banking","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/artificial-intelligence-in-corporate-cloud-banking\/","title":{"rendered":"Artificial Intelligence in Corporate Cloud banking"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>The strategic deployment of artificial intelligence in banking and the <a href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/the-future-of-digital-payments-2022-and-onwards\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"178\">digital payments sector<\/a>, in general, can offer extensive benefits. Banks can gain meaningful results from implementing computer vision, natural language processing, and machine learning.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Implementation of artificial intelligence in the banking sector can assist in improving back-office operations, <a href=\"https:\/\/searchcustomerexperience.techtarget.com\/definition\/customer-experience-CX?_gl=1*1brefsi*_ga*MjE4NjE5MzI5LjE2MzY2OTI0MzQ.*_ga_TQKE4GS5P9*MTYzNjcwMTA4MS4yLjAuMTYzNjcwMTA4MS4w&amp;_ga=2.28379257.432963458.1636692434-218619329.1636692434\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">overall customer experiences<\/a>, and employee satisfaction. Additionally, the cost savings arising from the use of AI in the payments industry are significant.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>According to a report by <a href=\"https:\/\/www.accenture.com\/_acnmedia\/PDF-138\/Accenture-Banking-AI.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Accenture<\/a>, payment processing companies can record an increase of up to five times in financial transaction volume or transactions having the exact headcount. That\u2019s how much AI can impact the corporate cloud banking sector.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_45 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc